  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374400/extras/314ab9996d00cacc72793821a7c55560.avif?t=1770517065\" width=600 height=125 /></span><br><br><strong>This is a rage game!</strong><br><br><strong>Where is my parking spot!?</strong>: Drive around parking lots to find your special spot, race against the clock or set a record. You <strong>MUST</strong> get to that special parking spot! <i>Also... when you use the brakes it also leaks brake fluid? That's normal right?</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374400/extras/fc483bcb1894467fd0a6ec78dce74cd6.avif?t=1770517065\" width=600 height=125 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Set new records by going as fast as you can!<br></li><li> Try to beat you time per-level and show who's the best!<br></li><li> Most levels have secret ways to get faster, try to find them!<br></li><li> Times saved to the Steam Cloud!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374400/extras/02abdc74a4777e3c008c02eca360eae6.avif?t=1770517065\" width=600 height=125 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Parking in a spot next to you? <i>NOPE</i> You need that special spot!<br></li><li> Park at a store, even on top of a parking garage, and beyond!<br></li><li> Parking can be complex and takes skill to master, Up for the challenge? or are you a <strong>WIMP?!</strong>.<br></li><li> Look out for the pesky drivers who love to backup in the parking lot!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374400/extras/e9de6bf3afe663f12486edf3041d22a0.avif?t=1770517065\" width=600 height=125 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Make your car look cool.<br></li><li> Unlock achievements to earn more skins!<br></li><li> Parking has never been cooler, just wait when they see you pull into that spot in style!<br></li><li> Paint jobs that make you look so cool, even the parking lots get jealous.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374400/extras/055c83e5921c64a12826189b1db2c4cd.avif?t=1770517065\" width=600 height=125 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374400/extras/65d60248974176c3a724d3f64427d720.avif?t=1770517065\" width=256 height=256 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374400/extras/38ad3dd2318f280d6bfcb4ff83580479.avif?t=1770517065\" width=256 height=256 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374400/extras/df9024cbeaa8ffda14cbce30befd99ac.avif?t=1770517065\" width=256 height=256 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374400/extras/d7d7daad7a25884f06328cb7af078ff6.avif?t=1770517065\" width=256 height=256 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374400/extras/314ab9996d00cacc72793821a7c55560.avif?t=1770517065\" width=600 height=125 /></span><br><br><strong>This is a rage game!</strong><br><br><strong>Where is my parking spot!?</strong>: Drive around parking lots to find your special spot, race against the clock or set a record. You <strong>MUST</strong> get to that special parking spot! <i>Also... when you use the brakes it also leaks brake fluid? That's normal right?</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374400/extras/fc483bcb1894467fd0a6ec78dce74cd6.avif?t=1770517065\" width=600 height=125 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Set new records by going as fast as you can!<br></li><li> Try to beat you time per-level and show who's the best!<br></li><li> Most levels have secret ways to get faster, try to find them!<br></li><li> Times saved to the Steam Cloud!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374400/extras/02abdc74a4777e3c008c02eca360eae6.avif?t=1770517065\" width=600 height=125 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Parking in a spot next to you? <i>NOPE</i> You need that special spot!<br></li><li> Park at a store, even on top of a parking garage, and beyond!<br></li><li> Parking can be complex and takes skill to master, Up for the challenge? or are you a <strong>WIMP?!</strong>.<br></li><li> Look out for the pesky drivers who love to backup in the parking lot!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374400/extras/e9de6bf3afe663f12486edf3041d22a0.avif?t=1770517065\" width=600 height=125 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Make your car look cool.<br></li><li> Unloc